            , was indicted for <rs id="t18010415-85-off477" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18010415-85-off477" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18010415-85-off477" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18010415-85-cd478" type="crimeDate">27th of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010415-85-off477 t18010415-85-cd478"></join>, four yards of tiffany, value 10s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18010415-85-victim921" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Bossam
                        <interp inst="t18010415-85-victim921" type="surname" value="Bossam"></interp>
